Usage: deleteNetFromNetGroup [-help] <netGroupName>
                             -net {netName | netNameList}

-help                                    # Prints out the command usage
<netGroupName>                           # Specifies the name of the net group.
                                         # You can use wildcards (*?) with this
                                         # parameter. (string, required)
-net {netName | netNameList}             # Specifies the name of the net(s).
                                         # You can use wildcards (*?) with this
                                         # parameter. (string, required)